<plot>Apollo Remix is a re-edit of original NASA footage (in the public domain) into a work that shifts the emphasis from the moon back to the earth - specifically the view of earth from space. Ultimately, this short is a re-presentation of the earth without borders, as it is seen by astronauts in space.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?043563</url></doc>
